Poka¿ na wyœwietlaczu LCD klawiatury Logitech
Allows showing currently selected graph values in Logitech keyboard LCD display.

Wskazówki:
- You must activate and select desired graph to get access to this option.
- You may hold <Shift> button pressed on your keyboard while changing this option to change it synchronically for all graphs.
- You may select the font for Logitech keyboard LCD output in the adjacent dropdown list.
- You may scroll the text displayed in Logitech keyboard LCD using 4 Logitech keyboard soft buttons. Vertical and horizontal scrolling positions can be reset by pressing up/down or left/right scroll buttons simultaneously.
